overview: "The user initiated a request for a comprehensive review of their
  sleep questionnaire application, including its database and API endpoints,
  against the provided acceptance criteria and detailed specification. The agent
  conducted a thorough examination of the codebase, identifying several areas
  where the implementation fell short of the requirements. A detailed plan was
  then generated, categorizing the missing features by priority. The agent then
  proceeded to implement the first high-priority item: integrating a 1-10
  tiredness severity scale into the questionnaire. This involved updating data
  types, validation schemas, the UI component for the questionnaire section, and
  both the web and PDF report generation to display critical safety warnings for
  high severity scores. The agent is currently in the process of implementing
  the next item on the plan."
